column2: New York City Labor Force Data, Seasonally Adjusted
New York State Department of Labor, Current Employment Statistics. Data seasonally adjusted by New York City Office of Management and Budget

As of the January 2018 reference month (released March 9, 2018), NYC OMB has altered its seasonal adjustment methodology.  For details see http://www1.nyc.gov/assets/omb/downloads/pdf/2stepSAmethodology.pdf

As of the May 2021 reference month (released July 2, 2021), NYC OMB has altered its seasonal adjustment methodology.  For details see http://www1.nyc.gov/assets/omb/downloads/pdf/nycomb_covidoutliers.pdf
